      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RED DIRT ROAD (2) shapes well for this on his slick win a few runs back, getting around this track over 520m in 29.82 then hitting the frame in both runs since. Can measure up again if runs up to recent best times. BROWNLOW (3) box seated before sticking on well to finish 4.5 lengths away in third (30.60) at this track in a Mix 5 over 520m. Will give a great sight again. LITTLE CLIFFY (5) won again in another strong performance after stalking the pace to make it back to back wins, scoring by a nose (30.33) at this track over 520m. The form from his last run stacks up well. Leading player again. GYPSY KING (1) placed last time and is worth some thought.",
